      },
      {
        title: "Information Usage",
        content: `We use collected information to:
        • Provide, maintain, and improve game services
        • Save your game progress and creations
        • Send game updates and important notifications
        • Analyze game usage to optimize user experience
        • Prevent fraud and abuse`
      },
      {
        title: "Information Sharing",
        content: `We do not sell your personal information. We only share information:
        • With your explicit consent
        • To comply with legal requirements
        • To protect Sprunki Game and users' rights and safety`
      },
      {
        title: "Data Security",
        content: `We take multiple measures to protect your information:
        • Use encryption for data transmission
        • Regular security reviews and updates
        • Strict internal access controls
        • Data backup and recovery mechanisms`
      },
      {
        title: "User Rights",
        content: `You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
